cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.DS, cs.CY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper deals with cybersecurity posture and analyzing data to understand it. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also likely as the data was collected by CAIDA's network telescope. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possibility as the paper deals with analyzing time series data related to cybersecurity. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper proposes formalizing the concept of cybersecurity posture and characterizing it through statistical properties of time series data. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possibility as the paper deals with cybersecurity and its implications on society.
